---
// The Shift Section - Explaining the need for systems in the AI age
---

<section class="py-[var(--space-5)] container-fluid relative overflow-hidden">
  
  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    
    <!-- Left: The Problem -->
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 opacity-70">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-medium text-text">Critical Shift</span>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-[var(--step-3)] leading-[1.1] mb-6">
        The "Website" Era<br />
        <span class="text-text/40">Is Officially Dead.</span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg mb-8">
        AI has democratized creation. The internet is flooded with infinite content, noise, and generic templates. 
        <br/><br/>
        In this new landscape, a static brochure website is a liability. It waits for traffic that never comes and converts no one. 
        It is a <span class="text-text/60 font-semibold line-through">digital business card</span>.
      </p>

      <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-panel/5 border border-text/5 backdrop-blur-sm max-w-md">
        <h3 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-4 font-bold">The Old Standard</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-text/60">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-500/50">✕</span> Static Information
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-500/50">✕</span> Waits for leads to contact you
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-500/50">✕</span> Manual follow-up (when you remember)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-red-500/50">✕</span> Sleeps when you sleep
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: The Solution (System) -->
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <div class="absolute -inset-10 bg-[radial-gradient(circle,rgb(var(--accent)/0.15),transparent_70%)] blur-[50px] pointer-events-none"></div>

      <div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-[rgb(var(--panel))] soft-border p-8 lg:p-10 shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] relative group">
        <!-- Glow effect on hover -->
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-text/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition duration-700 pointer-events-none rounded-[2rem]"></div>
        
        <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-[var(--step-2)] mb-2 text-text">
          Enter The <span class="text-[rgb(var(--accent))] architect-glow">System</span>.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-muted mb-8">
          You don't need a designer. You need an Architect. We build authoritative ecosystems that operate independently of your time.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-panel/5 border border-text/10 group-hover:border-[rgb(var(--accent)/0.3)] transition duration-500">
            <div class="mt-1 p-2 rounded-lg bg-[rgb(var(--accent)/0.1)] text-[rgb(var(--accent))]">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20M12 2a10 10 0 0 1 10 10 10 10 0 0 1-10 10 10 10 0 0 1-10-10 10 10 0 0 1 10-10z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-text mb-1">Omnipresent Authority</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted">Positioned as the only logical choice in your niche, everywhere, all at once.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-panel/5 border border-text/10 group-hover:border-[rgb(var(--accent)/0.3)] transition duration-500 delay-100">
            <div class="mt-1 p-2 rounded-lg bg-[rgb(var(--accent)/0.1)] text-[rgb(var(--accent))]">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-text mb-1">AI-Driven Capture</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted">Smart agents engage visitors, qualify intent, and book revenue instantly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

           <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-panel/5 border border-text/10 group-hover:border-[rgb(var(--accent)/0.3)] transition duration-500 delay-200">
            <div class="mt-1 p-2 rounded-lg bg-[rgb(var(--accent)/0.1)] text-[rgb(var(--accent))]">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-text mb-1">Perpetual Motion</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-muted">A machine that generates, nurtures, and closes while you focus on delivery (or sleep).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
